text:
so you could do:
```
--for loop code--
&lt;div class="content-{{loop.index}}"&gt;
{{item.story_text}}
&lt;/div&gt;
---rest of code --
```

then your output would be something like
```
&lt;div class="content-1"&gt;content&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="content-2"&gt;content&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="content-3"&gt;content&lt;/div&gt;
```
